# PayNode Meta Repository Ignore Rules
# We only track meta-assets and global configs

# Ignore everything
*

# Allow specific meta files
!public/
!scripts/
!CHANGELOG.md 
!GEMINI.md 
!paynode-config.json 
!README.md 
!SDK_SPECIFICATION.md
!.gitignore

# Ignore sub-repo contents (handled by their own git)
apps/
packages/
node_modules/
.env
